[3] Ukraine
Date: Tue 13 Mar 2012
Source: Ukrainian Radio News [edited]
http://www.nrcu.gov.ua/index.php?id=148&listid=166196


Number of suspected measles cases exceeds 5000
-------------------------------------------
According to the press service of the Ukrainian Health Ministry, a total of 5127 cases of measles have been reported in Ukraine since the beginning of 2012, including 162 over the last 24 hours.

The greatest numbers of measles cases were reported in Ukraine's western regions, particularly in Ivano-Frankivsk region -- 89, Lviv region -- 15, Zakarpattia region -- 15, Ternopil region --13, Volyn region -- 3, and Rivne region --1. 4 cases of suspected measles were reported in Kyiv.

